Package pt.unl.fct.di.dbc4j

Class Summary
ContractLogic Class for emulating first order logic operators and quantifiers.
ContractMemory Class for memorizing the old state of an object or member.
ContractRules Class for providing run-time configuration to the contract rules.
DesignByContract DesignByContract class.
Rules Class for representing contract rules.
RulesLoader Class for loading contract rules from a properties file.
 

Enum Summary
CheckLevel Enumeration that expresses the level of run-time checking performed.
MethodType Enumeration that differenciates different types of method (regarding assertion implementation).
 

Exception Summary
ContractException Abstract class for contract design exceptions.
CopyConstructorException Exception used when trying to evaluate an overrided public assertion, while the super class has no copy constructor.
InvalidVisibilityException Exception used when trying to evaluate an assertion with non-public, non-private visibility.
InvariantException Exception used when a class invariant does not hold in a certain execution context.
NonCloneableException Exception used when trying to use the 'remember' mecanism on a non-cloneable class.
PostconditionException Exception used when a method postcondition does not hold in a certain execution context.
PreconditionException Exception used when a method precondition does not hold in a certain execution context.
RulesFileException Exception used for problems regarding the rules file.
